11 "§2180.38 Unlicensed healthcare facility disclosure
12 (A) Any pregnancy resource center which provides healthcare services shall
13 clearly and conspicuously disclose the following statement in the manner described
14 in this Section: "This center is not a licensed medical facility regulated by the
15 Louisiana Department of Health."
16 (B) The disclosure required by this Section shall meet all of the following:
17 (1) Be printed on durable signage material that is at least sixteen inches by
18 twenty inches, and the text shall be no smaller than thirty-six point type.
19 (2) Be posted in each patient admission area, patient waiting room, and
20 patient consultation room.
21 (3) Be included on the pregnancy resource center's website homepage, if
22 applicable, in a clear and conspicuous manner.
23 (4) Be included in any print, digital, or broadcast advertisements that
24 reference healthcare services.
25 (5) Be stated on any intake forms provided to clients.
26 (6) Be provided in English.
27 (7) Be provided in any other language in which the pregnancy resource center
28 provides services or advertises."
